{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_13134.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103401,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story12","chara":[{"id":103401,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-1"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.2},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-2"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"I had a feeling you were going to leave."},{"chara":[{"id":103401,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-3"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"As I do not share the same beliefs as you, I refuse@to allow my presence to cause rifts in the Clan."},{"chara":[{"id":103401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-4"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"Therefore, I must depart."},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-5"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Thank you for everything..."},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-6"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"You helped me so much,@especially with Himena Aika..."},{"chara":[{"id":103401,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-7"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"...My true intention back then..."},{"chara":[{"id":103401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-8"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"...was to not see you besmirched, Lady Shizuka."},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-9"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"What do you mean?"},{"chara":[{"id":103401,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-10"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"The pride of the Tokime Clan―to protect this land@and its people, even at the cost of our own lives―"},{"chara":[{"id":103401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-11"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"It was too beautiful and incorruptible@for someone like me to behold,"},{"chara":[{"id":103401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-12"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"and yet when I did, I felt no anger or envy,@not even in the slightest."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":103401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-13"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"Instead, I felt hope."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":103401,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-14"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"I felt that if the world was pure enough"},{"chara":[{"id":103401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-15"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"to allow the Tokime Clan to fulfill its purpose,"},{"chara":[{"id":103401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-16"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"then the chains of resignation@within me could finally be broken."},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-17"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-18"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Have I been able to fulfill that hope, Asahi...?"},{"chara":[{"id":103401,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-19"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"Truth be told, I feel you haven't."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-20"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"I see..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":103401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-21"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"You are on the verge of being engulfed@by the world's evils, just as I am..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102501,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-22"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"...?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102501,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-23"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"So I must resist...evil?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103401,"motion":300,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-24"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"To give you a clear answer@would contradict my purpose,"},{"chara":[{"id":103401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-25"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"and I am certain that I would@be of little assistance to you."},{"chara":[{"id":103401,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-26"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"All I can do is wait and see@what becomes of the Tokime Clan."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":0,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-27"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Very well."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":100,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-28"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Thank you again for everything, Asahi."},{"chara":[{"id":103401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-29"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"Once this is over, will you welcome me back?"},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-30"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Of course I will. You're family."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-31"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"And you're very important to me, too."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":103401,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-32"}],"nameRight":"Asahi","textRight":"Then I await that day with great anticipation."},{"autoTurnLast":1,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":103401}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":102501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-33"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-34"}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"So we do need to teach people@righteousness after all..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bgm":"stop","textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":2,"bg":"black","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"white","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"[textBlack:―Interview Record―@Sunao Toki]","narrationCoverOpacity":0,"narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut","turnChangeOutTime":0.2},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"black","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":1,"pos":2,"posX":80}],"item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1,"path":"resource/scenario/img/51030_fishing_homura/51030_homura_dairy.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"bgFront"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"bgm":"bgm20_song10","chara":[{"id":102701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-36"}],"nameNarration":"Sunao","narrationCoverOpacity":0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":100,"progressNarration":"[textBlack:\"I'm not famous, and yet I feel@so nervous at the thought of@being interviewed...\"]","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-37"}],"progressNarration":"[textBlack:\"Given my demeanor, people express@disbelief that I used to be an@assassin targeting those who@would intervene with the@Tokime Village's doings.\"]"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-38"}],"progressNarration":"[textBlack:\"But as I said in the past,@there's no avoiding the truth.@My regrets are carved deep@into my very being...\"]"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102701,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-39"}],"progressNarration":"[textBlack:\"That's why...for all that I tried@to kill her, I want to help Shizuka@elevate the Tokime Clan towards@the ideal she strives to attain.@Since we've known each other for@so long, I feel a strong sense of@duty towards watching over her.\"]"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":102701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-40"}],"progressNarration":"[textBlack:\"Unfortunately, however, I'm just@a country girl compared to Charu,@so there's not much I can do to@help her navigate city life.\"]"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-41"}],"progressNarration":"[textBlack:\"Still, no matter how much I help@our clan, the fact I tried to kill@them will never be erased...\"]"},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-42"}],"progressNarration":"[textBlack:\"Perhaps the reason I'm so drawn@towards caring for children and@elders is because I seek@repentance for my sins...\"]"},{"autoTurnLast":6.5,"chara":[{"id":102701,"motion":0,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-43"}],"progressNarration":"[textBlack:\"I hate myself for thinking that way...@But I will strive nevertheless@to aid those who need me now.\"]"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102701}]},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-44","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_102931/vo_full_102904-10-43"}],"progressNarration":"[textBlack:\"If I could have just one wish,@it would be to enjoy my@adolescence so much that my@dark past fades away.\"]"},{"autoTurnLast":2,"bgm":"stop","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51030_fishing_homura/51030_homura_dairy.jpg","visible":"hide"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
